SFL.Name: DeviceConfig
SFL.Description: The value of the sensor resistor

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ if any cell is being balanced. Automatically clears to ‘0’ if no cells are being balanced.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when OZ3710 internal temperature exceeds ~120°C. Cell balancing is halted. Automatically clears to ‘0’ when OZ3710 internal temperature is less than ~90°C.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when OZ3710 internal temperature exceeds ~120°C. Cell balancing is blocked when this bit is ‘1’. To re-enable cell balancing, clear to ‘0’ by writing ‘1’ to this bit.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ if there is an I2C timeout.Clear to ‘0’ by writing ‘1’.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when watchdog times out.Clear to ‘0’ by writing ‘1’.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when DOC comparator detects DOC.Clear to ‘0’ by writing ‘1’.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when DOC comparator detects DOC.Automatically clears to ‘0’ when no DOC.

SFL.Name: Scan
SFL.Description: Automatically sets to ‘1’ when power on reset occurs. Clear to ‘0’ by writing ‘1’.
